== Births == * [[Keichō]] 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1606]] {{ill|April 16|ja|4月16日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Nanbu Shigenao|ja|南部重直|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the 2nd lord of the Morioka Domain (died [[1664]]). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 20th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1735]] {{ill|April 1|ja|4月1日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Katō Chien|ja|加藤千蔭|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, a Kokugaku scholar and waka poet (died [[1808]]).
== Deaths == * [[Emperor Richū]] 6th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[405]] {{ill|April 29|ja|4月29日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Emperor Ritsuchū|ja|履中天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the 17th Emperor of Japan.
