== Events == * {{ill|Taikang|ja|太康_(晋)|zh|太康_(西晋)|ko|태강_(서진)|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[280]] {{ill|May 1|ja|5月1日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – In this year, the grandson Hao of Wu surrendered to the Jin, leading to the unification of China under Jin. * [[Gangyō]] 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[878]] {{ill|April 21|ja|4月21日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – The Gangyō Rebellion occurred in Dewa, when a revolt by the Ezo erupted and attacked Akita Castle. * [[Keichō]] 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1598]] {{ill|April 20|ja|4月20日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – A famed flower-viewing event was held at Daigo. Toyotomi Hideyoshi and Hideyori had their final hanami. * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}} [[1868]] {{ill|April 7|ja|4月7日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) – The Meiji government established high-Ranking signboards known as the "Gobō no Keiji" at the outset of its reforms.
